1. Core Principle

A “lucky gift” is a low-cost, high-resonance artifact delivered at the right moment along a user’s trajectory.

Not expensive.
Not flashy.

But:
	•	timely
	•	meaningful
	•	slightly unexpected
	•	feels “chosen for them”

⸻

