6. Timing engine (this is critical)

A good gift at the wrong time = useless
A decent gift at the right time = powerful

Trigger conditions
	•	repeated failure pattern detected
	•	hesitation / stall
	•	rapid progress (boost moment)
	•	emotional shift
	•	novelty decay (boredom)

⸻

7. Delivery style

Do NOT over-explain.

Bad:

“Based on your trajectory analysis…”

Good:

“This might be your next move.”

Or:

drop an image, phrase, or idea
let them connect it

